Author: akshayp
Title: [ANN] [PRE-ICO] SET - Introducing Blockchain to Ecofriendly Product Marketplace
Body: Save Environment Token, commonly known as SET dedicates its efforts towards saving Humanity from the ill-effects of pollution and global warming.  SET aims to achieve this through multiple strategies, one of them being e-bikes. E-bikes are bicycles that have advanced built-in features. These features allow the users to track the location of the bike via a GPS signal which ties via software to a dedicated control center. Location tracking helps users keep track of the bike for the well-being of their friends and family. It also protects bike lenders from theft and loss of property.  SET’s Public Bicycle Sharing (PBS) is an exciting concept where bikes are placed strategically in a network of stations. These bikes are readily available for public use, offering unmatched affordability and convenience.  PBS offers a straightforward solution that allows residents and employees to ditch traffic. The model is well-thought out to remedy the problem of finding parking spaces. It helps save time, money and the environment. PBS, like many bicycle share system across the world, offers free rides for the first 30–40 minutes of travel. It encourages people to ditch polluting vehicles and go green. It’s focus also relies on promoting a healthy lifestyle. This concept has the potential to revolutionize the way people commute. It benefits not only companies but students and universities as well. It will also help curb pollution levels across cities by improving both indoor and outdoor air quality. Added benefits include a drop in obesity among residents which decreases health-risks, enhancing the overall quality of life.  To read more Click here  https://scontent-bom1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/37036987_2106138146321629_4424121949047750656_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&oh=43efcc429ae58e9a4bf8ce197188aa72&oe=5B9DAE8B

Author: GarrySingh
Title: [ANN] [PRE-ICO] SET - Introducing Blockchain to Ecofriendly Product Marketplace
Body: SET Plans to Install 100,000 Outdoor Air Pollution Controllers Across India  SET has partnered with Strata Enviro Pvt Ltd. to provide free air pollution controllers at various public locations. This project has been possible with the help of a unique revenue and sustainability model.  Air pollution gives way to dangerous and fatal diseases like lung cancer, Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD), stroke, acute respiratory diseases and more.  Almost 90% of these deaths occur among people that belong to low and middle-income countries. The PM 2.5 and PM 10 particles present in air pollution causes severe damage to the respiratory system by getting lodged in the lungs. The burning of fossil fuels releases life-threatening chemicals in the air that can cause a multitude of health problems.  SET has planned to install 100,000 Outdoor Air Pollution Controllers across India in densely populated areas such as traffic signals, bus stands, schools, hospitals, malls, banks, petrol pumps, airports, IT parks and similar locations. In fact, the company has already installed several Outdoor Air Pollution Controllers in high-density areas across India.   To read more about the article, click here: https://medium.com/save-environment-token/set-plans-to-install-100-000-outdoor-air-pollution-controllers-across-india-9ca11b502d1f
